ent-AU14WeaponFlamerM240A2HAZOPS = M240A2 heavy incinerator unit
    .desc = The USCMC's answer to WY's Flammerwerfer 3. Much more effective than the standard M240, but inflicts a movement penality. Typically issued to HAZOPS.
